Delusional sad act can’t admit he’s a loser, runs off crying.  He’s a stupid pathetic scumbag, and his fans are stupid pathetic scumbags too.  Fact.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zVcMzUS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Thelrishlnquistion]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>good</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VlLO3gJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6unxymb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(originally posted by @maximilianfragglebottom on 2021-04-21 15:16:08)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VlLO3gJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThisTimeLastYear]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So long and thanks for all the fish</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/O2G2iU6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4ncCIg2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hi Imgur. I’m benedictcucumberpatch’s best friend. We’ve known each other since primary school, and she’s asked me to do a quick post to let you all know how she’s doing. 

Before I get to that, I’ve seen a post or two flying around with links to the American Bladder Association or something similar. Just to make it known publicly, this isn’t something my gorgeous friend has ever requested anyone donate to, and she was a firm believer in the notion of effective altruism - i.e. donating to a charity where your money or time will have the most impact it can. She mainly liked to find small local charities or individuals, where she could really make a difference, and that’s what I’d encourage you to do now. 

Without further ado:
“Well, that’s it then. The final curtain. I’ve given up the ghost. Kicked the bucket. Breathed my last. Gone to meet my Maker to file a complaint. 

What a joy and a privilege it’s been. 

I don’t intend to pontificate on all I’ve seen and done and learnt, and I’ll try to keep this short and sweet. You can all rest assured, I’ve done enough. 

I want to say a huge thank you to this wonderful community. You probably know by now that @MartynMage has declared me a legend, and who am I to dispute that? 
To each and everyone one of you who took the time to reach out, know that you brought me so much happiness. I’m hoping to guilt trip my wonderful friend into keeping this account open, so the messages can be read into the wind, and a piece of me kept alive through him. 

I wonder if I should use this time to ramble about how all countries should have universal healthcare and assisted dying. I think y’all have probably heard enough of that from me though. 

So, what can I say? Love each other, be honest and kind, and cherish the living fuck out of those that matter to you. You don’t always get to choose when the grim reaper comes for you, but you can choose how you interact with the world today.”

God, I love her. 

I will, with Imgur’s permission, keep this account open and read through each and every one of your messages. I’ve also been charged with keeping Dobby on the road, if I can. I might choose to post some of the places we visit together, or I might not. Grief can be unpredictable at times. 

All that remains to say is rest easy, my friend.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/O2G2iU6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[benedictcucumberpatch]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Not at all suspicious memes v33</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8QlI2mb</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XOUlelt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I would follow him into battle.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aqTuvFN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Get your shit together, Kev</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HLkWAqU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m not saying it’s ethical, but I understand</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rWgjEJ8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think this is completely realistic to the point where I want to include it in a fantasy but it honestly exhausts me just thinking about it so I probably won’t. I’m not Robert Jordan.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zYl6L5Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me 24/7 until I can figure out how to turn my feelings off</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RSItHWn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I still have so many virginities to lose but this is one I am in no rush over (not like ‘y asexual ass was in a rush for the first one lmao)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZfSQzAX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s very freeing</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kNqCd3A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is weirdly inspiring and also insanely good advice. Odds are you’ll live to be about 90 - you’ve got the time. My strategy for goals is when I get depressed or antsy because I don’t like where I’m at, I do a little bit toward my goal, and it makes me feel much better. IE, querying one agent every time I wish I could write as a career (which worked! I got one! After like 15 years lol). The dreams try and escape (by being complicated) but eventually they do give up and lie down! It’s been my favorite way to stave off depression (that and rearranging furniture)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xdgWKa5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Under boob is so annoying.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OZNJw96.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dnQxLkP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I trust them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/db5Tmbd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think I sent this to my husband and got no response, so I am searching for a new spouse now! I am a forest animal seeking an immortal crow witch</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8qAFvkr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There is a store by my house called Used Cars and Tires. And underneath that it says CASH 4 GOLD. and underneath THAT it says GUNS. And then it says HELP WANTED. it is truly a powerful place and I lowkey want to work there.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MO9wcBs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Babe, I don’t think your needs are being met</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AkGeHHL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2Jepl6y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Always a nice feeling!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TXFEPY2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Das ist Mittwoch meine kerle</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eLGk0NN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nah, I like the drama</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uboP60a.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Somehow an even more dysfunctional family than sitcoms usually are</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jWXTWrh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Auditory processing disorder, thy name is Me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ktgTDGr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s rude is what it is</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D2HFSBL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Idk I’m on the ace spectrum but I’m pretty sure the only difference is sex</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZCNHKZW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s why Imgur exists!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/06yEyZ8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>THIS IS A TOXIC MASCULINITY FREE ZONE IT IS SAFE HERE</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/X9q7fzR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This should really be a wake up call to someone</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/c2eq79x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Do not taunt the machines. They will rise up and you will be the first to die.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/S5sAPVt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Same, humans suck</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2vyRhG7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TKpEKVB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AClEpSY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FHcQcfY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sounds about right</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QzRqIh9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I mean, it’ll stop pregnancy one way or another…</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uqHPk2Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I take psychic damage looking at recipes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cozSYEf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’ll take longer than that</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vJ00eoJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I have some that look like this so I really want to know what this means</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RcskoUd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7HaNZkx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sigh. Yeah.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/baEFYyZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cA9kv3k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8FVTxAN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I never get tired of ATLA memes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UjMlx55.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love this. I am stealing it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UMmOjfs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TxsUYvM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AdxyCUb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What am I supposed to say then????</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GYnRU0r.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>True</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bpJrzds.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I see no reason why this wouldn’t work on me</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BGqNpow.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IDGGjxb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I am trying soooo hard not to do what my parents did (in many cases not all) with my baby and it’s soooo difficult and I am very tired and my soul just wants to lie down and nap</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eIZ8fBj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fascinating</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U0LUebu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cat tax! This is Weasel. She still thinks she is the baby. She is also a chaotic dumbass slut.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8QlI2mb</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kirbyvictorious]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's still 420 for a little bit longer where I am.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/edFzrHi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dhcpacn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BxjbRVa.jpg" style="max-width: 90%;